{"ts":"2026-07-18T15:09:38.855Z","author":"codex-root","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/596\n\nThe 2026.7.18 CLI exits 0 for --ids containing valid and nonexistent IDs, but exposes only the matched subset and zero failures. Preserve partial-success behavior if desired, but make omission machine-detectable without client-side set differencing. Duplicate check searched all statuses for update-many, explicit IDs, nonexistent/missing/unmatched IDs. Closed pm-1h99 introduced --ids and explicitly documented that nonexistent IDs disappear; no item tracks surfacing that loss."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-ukml"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-596: update-many --ids must report nonexistent requested IDs"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Bulk explicit-ID mutations silently omit nonexistent IDs while reporting a fully successful matched subset, so agents cannot distinguish a complete request from a partial one."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","bulk-ops","data-integrity","gh-issue"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-18T15:09:38.855Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-18T15:09:38.855Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":90},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"update-many reports unmatched_ids and unmatched_count for explicit --ids; dry-run and apply envelopes agree; existing matched rows remain deterministic; CLI and contract tests cover mixed valid/missing IDs; GH-596 is resolved"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-1h99","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T15:09:38.855Z"},{"id":"pm-j2ig","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-18T15:09:38.855Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"5ad9b46e520fa4d45fbd1dc492da63dca1218ac8b7ff2c5b0f2e9988ef16883d","message":"Create from GH-596 after all-status duplicate check"}
